  "content": "\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-attachment-id=\"1842\" data-permalink=\"http://allthingsallergies.com/home-new/fullsizerender-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fullsizerender-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2825,3447\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"FullSizeRender\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fullsizerender-3.jpg?w=839\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"839\" height=\"1023\" data-id=\"1842\" src=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fullsizerender-3.jpg?w=839\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1842\" srcset=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fullsizerender-3.jpg?w=839 839w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fullsizerender-3.jpg?w=1678 1678w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fullsizerender-3.jpg?w=123 123w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fullsizerender-3.jpg?w=246 246w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fullsizerender-3.jpg?w=768 768w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/fullsizerender-3.jpg?w=1440 1440w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 839px) 100vw, 839px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2116\" data-permalink=\"http://allthingsallergies.com/home-new/facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16/\" data-orig-file=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1217,1490\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16.jpg?w=836\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"836\" height=\"1023\" data-id=\"2116\" src=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16.jpg?w=836\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2116\" srcset=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16.jpg?w=836 836w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16.jpg?w=123 123w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16.jpg?w=245 245w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16.jpg?w=768 768w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/facetune_25-09-2022-11-54-16.jpg 1217w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 836px) 100vw, 836px\" /></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-8f761849 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:100%\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center wp-block-paragraph\"><strong>Disclaimer</strong>: This collection of restaurants were thoughtfully included based on community reviews, available nutritional menus, and my personal experiences. The contents of this post should not be substituted for medical or professional advice. Please do your own research before dining at any of the following locations.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Fast Casual </h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-8f761849 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://bibibop.com\">Bibibop</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dedicated Free From Gluten + Nuts </li>\n\n\n\n<li>📌 <a href=\"https://bibibop.com/nutrition/\">Nutrition Guide</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>📍Multiple Locations</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.moonbowls.com\">Moon Bowls</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dedicated Free From Gluten + Dairy </li>\n\n\n\n<li>📌 <a href=\"https://www.moonbowls.com/faq\">Allergy FAQs and Nutrition Guide</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>📍Multiple Locations</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.thefatshallot.com/the-fat-shallots-new-site-is-coming-soon/\">The Fat Shallot</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Nut Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li>📍Lincoln Park, Evanston, Merchandise Mart</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.elephantandvine.com\">Elephant + Vine</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Vegan</li>\n\n\n\n<li>📍Lincoln Park</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">American</h3>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://veggiediner.com\">The Chicago Diner</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Vegan</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Lakeview</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://rh.com/us/en/chicago/restaurant\">3 Arts Club Cafe</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Gold Coast</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://thesmithrestaurant.com\">The Smith</a> </h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>📍River North</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://cindysrooftop.com\">Cindy&#8217;s</a> </h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>The Loop</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.armitagealehouse.com\">Armitage Alehouse</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free, Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.hogsalt.com\">Hogsalt Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Lincoln Park</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.giltbarchicago.com\">Gilt Bar</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free, Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.hogsalt.com\">Hogsalt Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>River North</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.auchevaldiner.com/chicago/home\">Au Cheval</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free, Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.hogsalt.com\">Hogsalt Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>West Loop</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.summerhouserestaurants.com\">Summer House Santa Monica</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating </li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.lettuce.com\">Lettuce Entertain You Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Lincoln Park</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Pizza + Pasta</h3>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://piccolosognorestaurant.com\">Piccolo Sogno</a> </h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Spokin Verified</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Fulton Market District</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://monteverdechicago.com\">Monteverde</a> </h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span> West Loop</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.rpmrestaurants.com/rpm-italian-chicago/\">RPM Italian</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.lettuce.com\">Lettuce Entertain You Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>River North</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.clubluckychicago.com\">Club Lucky</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Bucktown</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.cicciomio.com\">Ciccio Mio</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free, Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.hogsalt.com\">Hogsalt Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>River North</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.trivolitavern.com\">Trivoli Tavern</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free, Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.hogsalt.com\">Hogsalt Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Fulton Market District </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Asian Cuisine</h3>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.ramensan.com\">Ramen San</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Nut Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.lettuce.com\">Lettuce Entertain You Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Multiple Locations</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.sushisanrestaurant.com/\">Sushi San</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Nut Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.lettuce.com\">Lettuce Entertain You Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Multiple Locations</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://noburestaurants.com/chicago/home\">Nobu</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>📍Fulton Market District </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://aryabhavan.com\">Arya Bhavan</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Vegan, Gluten Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📌</span> <a href=\"https://aryabhavan.com/vegan-cooking-classes/\">Cooking Classes</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li>📍Little India</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.plantarestaurants.com/chicago-location/\">PLANTA Queen</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Vegan, Allergen Labeling</li>\n\n\n\n<li>📍River North</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Tacos + Tapas</h3>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://bartaco.com\">Bar Taco</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Extensive Allergen Menu</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://bartaco.com/nutrition/\">📌</a> <a href=\"https://bartaco.com/nutrition/\">Nutrition Guide</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Wicker Park</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.lonesomerose.com\">Lonesome Rose</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Spokin Verified</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span> Logan Square</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.bigstarchicago.com\">Big Star Tacos</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Wicker Park, Wrigleyville </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://penelopesvegantaqueria.com/home\">Penelope&#8217;s Vegan Taqueria</a> </h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Vegan</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Pilsen, Andersonville, River North</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.cafebabareeba.com\">Cafe Ba-Ba-Reeba!</a> </h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.lettuce.com\">Lettuce Entertain You Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Lincoln Park, River North</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Mediterranean </h3>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.abarestaurants.com/chicago\">Aba</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free, Highly Accommodating </li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.lettuce.com\">Lettuce Entertain You Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Fulton Market District</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.lyrarestaurant.com\">Lyra</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free, Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Fulton Market District</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://beatnikontheriver.com\">Beatnik on the River</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Extensive Allergen Menu</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>The Loop</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.emarestaurants.com\">Ēma</a> </h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating </li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.lettuce.com\">Lettuce Entertain You Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>River North, Glenview </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Steakhouses</h3>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.bavettessteakhouse.com\">Bavette&#8217;s</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free, Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.hogsalt.com\">Hogsalt Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>River North</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://gibsonssteakhouse.com\">Gibson&#8217;s Steakhouse</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating </li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Gold Coast, Rosemont</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.rpmrestaurants.com/rpm-steak-chicago/\">RPM Steak</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.lettuce.com\">Lettuce Entertain You Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>River North</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Breakfast / Lunch</h3>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.beatrixrestaurants.com\">Beatrix</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li>🍴<a href=\"https://www.lettuce.com\">Lettuce Entertain You Restaurant Group</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Multiple Locations</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://wheatsendcafe.com\">Wheat&#8217;s End Cafe</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dedicated Gluten Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Lakeview</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.doritedonuts.com\">Do-Rite Donuts</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free, Vegan Options</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Multiple Locations</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.beacondoughnuts.com\">Beacon Doughnuts</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Vegan</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Lincoln Park</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.puregreen.com\">Pure Green</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Multiple Locations</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.lacolombe.com\">La Colombe Coffee</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Nut Free, Dairy Free Options, Highly Accommodating</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📌</span> <a href=\"https://lacolombe.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/sections/360009784433-Ingredients\">Allergen FAQs</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Gold Coast, Lincoln Park, Wicker Park</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://fancyplantscatering.com\">Fancy Plants Cafe</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Vegan</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📍</span>Lakeview</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://foxtrotco.com/?srsltid=AfmBOoo-if3Gu7iqoXvfPs2n8x-l_VClKsukxzGu66nolcMzXRPBKV1a\">Foxtrot Market</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Carries Many Allergy Friendly Brands</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Multiple Locations</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Bakeries </h3>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.delsurchicago.com\">Del Sur Bakery</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dedicated Nut Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Ravensonwood</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"http://deflouredbakery.com\">DeFloured Bakery</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dedicated Gluten Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Ravenswood</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://simplysweetnutfree.com\">Simply Sweet Creations</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dedicated Nut Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Oak Lawn</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://bennisonscakes.com\">Bennison&#8217;s Bakery</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Peanut Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Evanston</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Frozen Desserts</h3>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.friogelato.com\">Frío Gelato</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dedicated Nut Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📌</span> <a href=\"https://www.friogelato.com/allergyfriendly\">Allergen Statement</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Evanston</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://jenis.com\">Jeni&#8217;s Ice Cream</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Allergy Protocol</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Multiple Locations</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://www.mikositalianice.com/allergens/\">Miko&#8217;s Italian Ice</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dairy Free</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Logan Square</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://avasitalianice.com\">Ava&#8217;s Italian Ice</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Dedicated Free From Dairy, Nuts, + Gluten</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Bucktown</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a href=\"https://vacascreamery.com\">Vaca&#8217;s Creamery</a></h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Vegan</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: -webkit-standard;font-size: medium;white-space: normal\">📌</span> <a href=\"https://vacascreamery.com/pages/allergies\">Allergen Guide</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><span style=\"white-space: normal;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: medium\">📍</span>Lincoln Square, Wicker Park</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Things To Do</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Yes, Chicago has an incredible food scene. But there is so much more to do in The Windy City than just eat and drink!  </p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">As a Chicago resident for the past 6 years, here’s where I’m taking my guests who come to town for a visit. </p>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Outdoor Activities</h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://shorelinesightseeing.com/architecture-river-tour/\">Chicago Architecture River Tour</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.lpzoo.org\">Lincoln Park Zoo</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.wrigleyrooftopsllc.com\">Wrigley Rooftops</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.greencitymarket.org\">Green City Farmer&#8217;s Market</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.chicagoparkdistrict.com/parks-facilities/beaches\">Lake Michigan</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.chicago.gov/city/en/sites/chicagoriverwalk/home.html\">Chicago Riverwalk</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://rooftopcinemaclub.com/chicago/venue/fulton-market/\">Fulton Rooftop Cinema</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.chicagobotanic.org\">Chicago Botanic Garden</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Performances + Shows</h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.secondcity.com\">Second City Comedy Club</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://chicago.zanies.com/#\">Zanie&#8217;s Comedy Club</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.broadwayinchicago.com\">Broadway in Chicago</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Museums</h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.artic.edu\">The Art Institute of Chicago</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sheddaquarium.org\">Shedd Aquarium</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.fieldmuseum.org\">Field Museum</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.adlerplanetarium.org\">Adler Planetarium</a> </li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.msichicago.org\">Museum of Science and Industry </a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://www.chicagohistory.org/visit-us/?utm_campaign=2025-2026+Campaign&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_medium=cpc&amp;utm_term=&amp;utm_content=&amp;cpn_id=69f1056f83e0628036093a43&amp;e_id=69ea66d30a38fd78e1e39b5c\">Chicago History Museum</a> </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Other Indoor Activities </h5>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.puttery.com/locations/\">Puttery Indoor Mini Golf</a></li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aliceandwonder.com\">Alice and Wonder &#8211; Design Your Own Hat</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-attachment-id=\"2966\" data-permalink=\"http://allthingsallergies.com/home-new/attachment/2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-450215437-e1716581112642.png\" data-orig-size=\"1080,227\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-450215437-e1716581112642.png?w=1024\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"215\" src=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-450215437-e1716581112642.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2966\" srcset=\"https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-450215437-e1716581112642.png?w=1024 1024w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-450215437-e1716581112642.png?w=150 150w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-450215437-e1716581112642.png?w=300 300w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-450215437-e1716581112642.png?w=768 768w, https://allthingsallergies.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-450215437-e1716581112642.png 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n",
